{"word":"ἐρωτάω","slug":"ἐρωτάω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἐρωτάω</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> epic verb <el>ἐρέω</el> ‘ask, inquire’]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp> ask,</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on querying for information <b><a href='B:470 15:23'>Mt 15:23</a>; <a href='B:470 16:13'>16:13</a>; <a href='B:480 4:10'>Mk 4:10</a>; <a href='B:490 22:68'>Lk 22:68</a>; <a href='B:500 1:19'>J 1:19</a>; <a href='B:500 4:47'>4:47</a>; <a href='B:500 5:12'>5:12</a>; <a href='B:500 16:5'>16:5</a>; <a href='B:510 1:6'>Ac 1:6</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp> ask,</b> in sense of making a request (frequently with connotation of an ameliorating tone for what might sound peremptory) <b><a href='B:480 7:26'>Mk 7:26</a>; <a href='B:490 5:3'>Lk 5:3</a>; <a href='B:490 8:37'>8:37</a>; <a href='B:500 16:26'>J 16:26</a>; <a href='B:510 10:48'>Ac 10:48</a>; <a href='B:510 18:20'>18:20</a>; <a href='B:570 4:3'>Phil 4:3</a>; <a href='B:590 4:1'>1 Th 4:1</a>; <a href='B:590 5:12'>5:12</a>; <a href='B:690 5:16'>1 J 5:16</a>; <a href='B:700 1:1'>2 J 5</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐρῶ\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἔσβεσα\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}